"     see \"Mupirocin: Drug information\"",
"    </a>",
"    and",
"    <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"UTD.htm?42/18/43300?source=see_link\">",
"     see \"Mupirocin: Pediatric drug information\"",
"    </a>",
"    )",
"   </p>",
"   <div class=\"list ubnlist drugH1Div drugBrandNames\" id=\"F198518\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Brand Names: U.S.",
